# pry-plus

Get up and going with a good set of pry tools right away.

Based on [RKing's pry-plus](https://github.com/rking/pry-plus). Updated with support for ruby 2.5 (requires Ruby version >= 2.3.0).

## Installation

In your `Gemfile`:

```ruby
gem 'kandr-pry-plus'
```

